        public static MR_RequestQueue newRequestQueue(Context context,
                              MR_HttpStack stack)
        Creates a default instance of the worker pool and calls MR_RequestQueue.start() on it.
        参数:
        context - A Context to use for creating the cache dir.
        stack - An MR_HttpStack to use for the network, or null for default.
        返回:
        A started MR_RequestQueue instance.
